    "body": "Allows for the customization of the short description created by environment modules. It is customized in the same manner as `naming_scheme`:\n\n``` yaml\nmodules:\n  enable:\n  - tcl\n  - dotkit\n  tcl:\n    naming_scheme: '{name}/{version}_{compiler.name}-{compiler.version}'\n    short_description_scheme: '{name}@{version} {compiler.name}@{compiler.version}'\n```\n",
